{"word":"G2849 - κολάζω - kolázō - kol-ad'-zo - Punish","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κολάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kolázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kol-ad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Punish"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தண்டி, ஆக்கினைக்குள்ளாகு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to lop, prune, as trees"},{"paragraph":"2. to check, curb, restrain"},{"paragraph":"3. to chastise, correct, punish"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <b>&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>kolos</b> (<i>dwarf</i>); properly to <i>curtail</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>chastise</i> (or <i>reserve</i> for infliction): - punish."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2849 - κολάζω - kolázō - kol-ad'-zo/2849\">G2849</a>, <a href=\"#/G2851 - κόλασις - kólasis - kol'-as-is/2851\">G2851</a>"}]}